Class Instance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheus.sdk.provisioning.Instance

  • public class Instance
extends java.lang.Object
    A Model representation of a Morpheus Instance It is used by GSON Decoder to convert JSON of the following structure into a java based Object.

    "id": 4,
    "accountId": 1,
